subject: Football
College Athletics
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: Trailing by 10 points in the first half, the Florida Gators awoke in time to welcome Texas A&M to its new league, spoiling the Aggies’ season opener before a crowd of 87,114 at Kyle Field.
